    <li><strong>Glossary Categories</strong> - Glossary categories are supported and can be used in glossary page, also set with a Shortcode. (<a href="http://jumpstartcto.com/glossary-shortcode/" target="new">Demo</a>), (<a href="http://jumpstartcto.com/glossary" target="new">Categories in Glossary Index</a>)</li>
